data.description: Welcome to your new home! This charming property offers the perfect blend of country living and convenient access to town amenities. Located on a corner lot, this delightful residence features three bedrooms with the potential for a fourth, making it an ideal space for a growing family or those in need of a home office or guest room. The home includes a welcoming living area, a well-appointed kitchen, and a dining space that exudes warmth and comfort. With 1.5 bathrooms, this home provides convenience and functionality for everyday living. Outside, the property boasts ample space for outdoor activities and gardening, creating an idyllic setting for enjoying the tranquility of country living. The surrounding area offers a peaceful escape from the hustle and bustle of city life while still providing easy access to town, ensuring a short commute to nearby amenities, schools, and entertainment. Don't miss the chance to make this cozy retreat your own!
